  "title": "Preschool Teacher English L2- Islandwide",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Develop and deliver an English-language curriculum that aligns with preschool education standards.</li>\n  <li>Use engaging teaching methods to encourage children’s language development, literacy, and communication skills.</li>\n  <li>Create a positive, safe, and stimulating classroom environment that encourages curiosity and learning.</li>\n  <li>Plan and conduct educational activities, including storytelling, games, music, arts, and crafts, to develop cognitive and motor skills.</li>\n  <li>Establish strong relationships with children, parents, and colleagues, ensuring clear communication regarding child development.</li>\n  <li>Attend parent-teacher meetings, staff meetings, and professional development sessions.</li>\n  <li>Maintain classroom discipline and ensure that children’s welfare and safety are prioritized.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Requirements:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Diploma or Degree in Early Childhood Education or equivalent.</li>\n  <li>Strong proficiency in spoken and written English.</li>\n  <li>Familiarity with Singapore's preschool education system and guidelines is an advantage.</li>\n  <li>Must have EDCA (L2)</li>\n</ul>\n<p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. All applications will be handled confidentially. By submitting your application, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and disclosure of your personal information to prospective employers.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Wecruit Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>EA License No: 20C0270</p>",
